race.comment: SUPERSTELLAR (11) has been racing over a bit further and wasn't disgraced last time. Best figures stack right up in this line-up and gets chance to break through. FAR REACHING (3) turned in a poor effort last time over 1450m at Mt Isa. Previous form was good for this and can improve sharply. SHEZ LETHAL (8) placed at first two runs from a spell then ran seventh at Longreach and wasn't far away. Went close here two back and can atone. TAHKIAN BUBBLES (5) was a last start placegetter and is well placed to find some winning form. LEGAL CHALLENGE (4) is yet to break through this campaign but hasn't been far away including a last start second over 1570m at Twin Hills. Expected to go close.
